data.description: The one dreams are made of. This renovated 3 bedroom 2 bath basement rancher features lots of natural light in the living room with a gas fireplace. The new leather granite countertops and LVP flooring in the eat-in kitchen has lots of room to prepare and serve your holiday meals.  Make memories in  the large basement rec room as you host movie nights, sleep overs and large family gatherings. The extra long one car garage is so much more with the extra space in the back and the laundry area. Get ready to spend a lot of time outdoors with 3 separate decks and an extra large corner lot including a smaller fenced in area for your family pet. Make home a place you want to be - Schedule your showing today!
